| # | Severity | Route / File | Issue |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | 🔴 Critical | `GET /api/leads/{lead_id}` | IDOR timing + RLS bypass risk |
| 2 | 🔴 Critical | `POST /api/auth/logout` | Conditional CSRF check — bypassable |
| 3 | 🔴 Critical | `POST /api/leads/scan` | Subreddit name injection → HTTP header injection |
